1.0 - About us
The server will be kept online as long as posible. The server will have unique features and items on it. The server will always be enjoyable for the people playing on it. __________________________________________________________________________
2.0 - Our Plan
Our plan is to make a very unique server. Our plan is to make a server that everyone will enjoy. Our plan is to make a server that will never be shut down. Our plan is to make a server that will always have a high ammount of people active. __________________________________________________________________________
3.0 - Donation Profit
We will purchase a reliabe VPS hosting system. We will purchase a reliable website domain system. We will use 75% of our donation profit on server related issues. We will use 25% of our donation profit on any other issues we may encounter. __________________________________________________________________________
